1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless
chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 2

16
00:01:44,550 --> 00:01:46,230
These people are here to escort me to the capital city?

17
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,360
Who asked them here?

18
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:50,760
Your father, of course.

19
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:53,080
I have refused him.

20
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:56,400
The capital city is not a good place.

21
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,040
Your mother died there.

22
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:05,000
You can live longer if you stay here.

23
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,760
But they are kneeling out of the door.

24
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:08,910
Leave them alone.

25
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:14,190
If they kneel there till they die, just bury them.

26
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,240
Uncle,

27
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:50,000
should I go to the capital city?

28
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:52,670
I remember your mom doing business

29
00:02:52,670 --> 00:02:53,600
in the capital city back then.

30
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:55,550
What else?

31
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,160
I can't remember.

32
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:04,720
So you mean

33
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,800
I should go.

34
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:09,390
To go or not to go, it's up to you.

35
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,600
My mom was killed in the capital city.

36
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:17,030
Are those killers still alive?

37
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,270
I have no idea.

38
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:24,320
I want to go to the capital city.

39
00:03:25,670 --> 00:03:27,520
What if it's dangerous?

40
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,960
Whatever you like.

41
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:39,270
What are you looking at?

42
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:43,030
I've been wondering recently.

43
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:46,160
Will your face remain young

44
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,270
when I am in my seventies or eighties.

45
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:06,670
Grandma!

46
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,160
Madam!

47
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,960
Those soldiers

48
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,470
won't eat anything.

49
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:16,550
I'm afraid if treated indifferently,
they won't remain loyal.

50
00:04:17,110 --> 00:04:17,760
Madam, I...

51
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,640
Eat!

52
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,320
I like this.

53
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,270
Today's dish is so fresh! Where does it come from?

54
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,040
He's asking you!

55
00:04:39,670 --> 00:04:41,440
Ha's nephew delivered it early in the morning.

56
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,830
Isn't Ha the one who usually delivers the vegetables?

57
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,200
How come his nephew came here today?

58
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,920
Ha's sick, so his nephew took his place.

59
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,880
Is there anything wrong?

60
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:49,950
Has Ha's nephew been here before?

61
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:52,200
It must be his first time.

62
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:53,760
Anything wrong?

63
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:57,720
Nothing.

64
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:02,880
Grandma.

65
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,790
I've finished eating. I'll leave now.

66
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:13,000
Madam, forgive me for being outspoken.

67
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:15,040
A dish of bamboo shoots counts for nothing.

68
00:05:15,350 --> 00:05:16,390
But he was acting

69
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:18,550
so arrogantly.

70
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:23,790
I'm just speaking out my mind.

71
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:36,950
Young Master!

72
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,000
Have you eaten the bamboo shoots?

73
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:39,760
Yes.

74
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,440
I...

75
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,110
Young Master, you...

76
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:52,070
Young Master, we don't know why.

77
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,230
Everyone suddenly

78
00:05:53,230 --> 00:05:54,110
started vomiting and having watery stools.

79
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,000
Come with me.

80
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,040
Take this.

81
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,440
Make them drink some milk.

82
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,510
They'll be fine after vomiting.

83
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,880
Here! Here! Here!

84
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,600
Where are the men in red?

85
00:06:17,110 --> 00:06:18,640
They asked about Ha's residence.

86
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,320
Then they left.

87
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,230
Here! Here! Here! There! There!

88
00:06:21,350 --> 00:06:21,950
Here! Here! Here!

89
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:23,270
Do make them drink more milk.

90
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,160
Everyone drinks some.

91
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,320
Here! Here! Here!

92
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,830
Wait!

93
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,480
What are you doing?

94
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:48,040
Kill the one who poisoned the dish.

95
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,600
Ha has delivered vegetables for us for many years.

96
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,920
He must have been held hostage.

97
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,040
If you rush in,

98
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,040
he will be killed.

99
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,230
Step aside!

100
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,480
I'm Fan Xian.

101
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:56,670
Step aside!

102
00:06:56,670 --> 00:06:57,920
What if it's a trick to lure you away?

103
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,880
Leave it to me.

104
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,510
Lend me a knife.

105
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:14,480
Ha!

106
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:32,000
You are the one who poisoned the bamboo shoots.

107
00:07:32,260 --> 00:07:33,780
=Teng Zijing, member of the Fourth Division
of the Investigator's Office of Nanqing=

108
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,200
Holy crap! Doraemon!

109
00:08:51,230 --> 00:08:52,000
You lose!

110
00:08:52,590 --> 00:08:54,200
You've put poison on your dagger.

111
00:08:56,110 --> 00:08:57,760
Before you die, I have a question for you.

112
00:08:58,790 --> 00:08:59,440
Why didn't you

113
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,440
let the soldiers in just now?

114
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,230
Risking your life

115
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,200
for a guy delivering vegetables,

116
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:13,710
it's not worth it.

117
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,880
What a coincidence!

118
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,320
My knife is also coated with poison.

119
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:27,400
Why are you fine with it?

120
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:28,710
To tell you the truth,

121
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,230
I've been poisoned since my childhood.

122
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:31,320
For me, ordinary poison

123
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,670
won't work.

124
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,280
You're the one who poisoned the dish.

125
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,520
Why didn't you use something highly toxic?

126
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,350
I only need to kill you.

127
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:43,280
Why do you have to kill me?

128
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:46,470
I received a secret order
from the Investigator's Office to kill the traitor.

129
00:09:48,110 --> 00:09:49,760
You're from the Investigator's Office.

130
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,520
If you kill me,

131
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:54,520
another assassin will come.

132
00:09:54,590 --> 00:09:55,840
If the Investigator's Office wants to kill someone,

133
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,520
he won't be able to...

134
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:01,760
Token for Director-General of the Investigator's Office.

135
00:10:03,110 --> 00:10:03,840
Where did you get it?

136
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,470
Fei Jie from the Third Division of the Investigator's Office

137
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:07,440
is my teacher.

138
00:10:10,150 --> 00:10:10,910
You don't believe me?

139
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,320
My mom died early.

140
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,230
I own no place in the Fan mansion.

141
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,520
I've lived in Danzhou since I was a child,

142
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,230
but my dad never visited me.

143
00:10:18,350 --> 00:10:19,200
My point is

144
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,400
how come a bastard son like me

145
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:22,150
has the quality

146
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,110
to become a traitor?

147
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:24,710
Only because I'm handsome?

148
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,790
You're a bastard?

149
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,230
So think about it.

150
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:30,590
I'm afraid there's something wrong with

151
00:10:30,590 --> 00:10:31,400
the secret order from the Investigator's Office.

152
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,400
We can really talk about it.

153
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,320
What do you think?

154
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:34,280
Moreover,

155
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,760
I also have a question for you.

156
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,440
The Fan mansion is managed according to strict rules.

157
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,790
How could you fool everyone

158
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,320
by pretending to be Ha's nephew

159
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,150
in you first appearance?

160
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:43,880
Who covered for you?

161
00:10:58,140 --> 00:10:58,150
=Butler Zhou, butler of the Fan mansion in Danzhou=

162
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:59,550
=Butler Zhou, butler of the Fan mansion in Danzhou=
You're the one who cooperated with the assassin

163
00:10:59,550 --> 00:10:59,620
=Butler Zhou, butler of the Fan mansion in Danzhou=
to mix the poison in the dish.

164
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:00,590
to mix the poison in the dish.

165
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,840
But it seems that

166
00:11:02,230 --> 00:11:03,470
grandma has already figured it out.

167
00:11:03,470 --> 00:11:05,060
=Madam Fan, Nanqing Earl Sinan Fan Jian's mother=

168
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:06,640
Madam!

169
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,880
Everything I did

170
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,400
is for the Fan family.

171
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:12,670
Take your time. Tell me everything.

172
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:17,710
Xian'er, kneel down and listen.

173
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,320
I was sent by Madam Liu Ruyu

174
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,350
to keep an eye on Fan Xian.

175
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,840
Once he arrives in the capital city,

176
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,400
he is sure to scramble for family properties.

177
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,790
Rather than let him ruin the family,

178
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:33,910
it's better to make sure

179
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:34,960
he never arrives in the capital city.

180
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:36,320
Moreover,

181
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:38,550
the Investigator's Office wanted to kill him this time.

182
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:39,960
I was just

183
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,110
giving them a hand.

184
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,000
That's right.

185
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:53,960
To protect the Fan family, we can't be softhearted.

186
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:14,080
Xian'er, you must keep that in mind.

187
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:16,230
You've grown up.

188
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:19,440
You must learn to be merciless.

189
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,080
I see.

190
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,000
Guards!

191
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,110
Madam!

192
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:32,520
Break his legs!

193
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:33,880
Throw him onto a fish boat!

194
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:37,440
He doesn't have to land the rest of his life.

195
00:12:37,590 --> 00:12:38,280
Yes.

196
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:44,110
No! No! No!

197
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:49,000
No! No! No!

198
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:49,790
Madam!

199
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,840
You've never liked Fan Xian
the whole time, haven't you?

200
00:12:54,470 --> 00:12:56,150
It's all an act!

201
00:12:57,350 --> 00:12:59,200
An act!

202
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:06,790
He had received a letter from Liu Ruyu,

203
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,230
asking him to cooperate with others

204
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,000
to kill you.

205
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,320
What do you think?

206
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:18,790
Madam Liu Ruyu

207
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,150
sends me gifts on every festival.

208
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:21,520
She's very kind to me.

209
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:22,590
I do remember that.

210
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:29,000
Right. A letter alone can't prove her guilty.

211
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:31,000
I'll ask your father

212
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:32,440
to investigate it further.

213
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,760
There must be an outcome.

214
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,550
Grandma!

215
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:40,150
What if I investigate it myself?

216
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:43,200
You want to go to the capital city?

217
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:46,960
Haven't we agreed that

218
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,590
you stay in Danzhou?

219
00:13:49,110 --> 00:13:51,760
I'll persuade your father.

220
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:53,150
Grandma!

221
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,670
Look what a big man I've grown into.

222
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,880
I have to witness the big world.

223
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,030
The first assassin has come,

224
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,200
and a second one will follow.

225
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,440
I've hidden for so long,

226
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,350
but they still won't let me go.

227
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:14,840
I might as well face them directly.

228
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:27,940
Have you made up your mind?

229
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:33,540
I'll come back after solving everything.

230
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:36,700
What if Liu Ruyu is behind the assassin?

231
00:14:42,220 --> 00:14:44,980
Then I'll tell her that

232
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:47,260
I'm not interested in the family properties.

233
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:50,700
I just taught you

234
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:53,300
to be merciless.

235
00:14:55,060 --> 00:14:57,140
Just be cautious!

236
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:00,540
Rest assured. I'm smart and flexible.

237
00:15:03,020 --> 00:15:04,100
When will you leave?

238
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:05,340
Tomorrow.

239
00:15:18,740 --> 00:15:19,620
Well,

240
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:23,260
I won't see you off tomorrow.

241
00:15:25,540 --> 00:15:28,860
I'm too old to stand separation.

242
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,940
Go back and get prepared.

243
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:53,620
Your grandma is really merciless.

244
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:55,780
She won't let him land the rest of his life.

245
00:15:58,660 --> 00:15:59,940
I've heard that

246
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,260
you two don't get along. Is that true?

247
00:16:01,660 --> 00:16:03,140
I've been hunted down by assassins since childhood,

248
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:04,860
so I was always worried that
I might bring trouble to my family.

249
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:06,780
So you asked her

250
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:08,260
to treat you indifferently.

251
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:10,460
But actually you were protecting her, right?

252
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:12,700
Now I'm leaving.

253
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:15,380
There's no need to act any more.

254
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,580
Thank you for helping me

255
00:16:17,860 --> 00:16:18,820
in the cooperation.

256
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:19,620
No need to thank me.

257
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:21,940
The Investigator's Office has sent
an urgent order via a flying pigeon,

258
00:16:21,940 --> 00:16:24,060
saying that the secret order to kill you is fake.

259
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:26,020
Someone wanted to get rid of you

260
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:27,740
by using the Investigator's Office.

261
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:28,500
Who?

262
00:16:29,140 --> 00:16:29,820
We're still investigating.

263
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:34,460
When I arrive in the capital city,

264
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:35,780
I can figure it out for sure.

265
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:41,780
Fan Xian, I need a favor from you.

266
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:42,980
Just say it.

267
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:44,500
Please kill me.

268
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:48,540
Pardon?

269
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:51,020
Please kill me.

270
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:56,580
What's your name?

271
00:16:56,940 --> 00:16:59,780
Teng Zijing from the Fourth Division
of the Investigator's Office.

272
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,180
Boss, I'd like to buy a pair of scissors.

273
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:08,380
Here is the money.

274
00:17:17,380 --> 00:17:18,580
I'll take the scissors.

275
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:30,880
He stole a lot of things.

276
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:32,830
I know.

277
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,640
Because it doesn't matter

278
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,350
whether the shop makes a profit or not.

279
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:40,160
You're here to protect me.

280
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:41,830
Yes.

281
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:55,590
Uncle, I'm leaving for the capital city.

282
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,520
OK.

283
