without your help.

290
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:21,350
I've already grown up.

291
00:18:21,710 --> 00:18:22,310
Good.

292
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:29,400
Ever since I could remember,

293
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,430
you've been guarding me.

294
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:33,230
As long as you're around,

295
00:18:33,230 --> 00:18:34,430
I fear nothing.

296
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:39,830
But that is not right.

297
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,190
What is not right?

298
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,830
Liu from the kitchen likes fishing.

299
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:51,000
Ma who guards the door loves watching girls.

300
00:18:51,590 --> 00:18:53,110
Everyone has a hobby.

301
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:58,350
And you? What do you like?

302
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,350
Nothing.

303
00:19:03,230 --> 00:19:04,760
Then do you have someone you like?

304
00:19:04,950 --> 00:19:07,160
Something you want to do?
Your own plan for life?

305
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,040
Sometimes, I just feel that

306
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,760
you are living for me.

307
00:19:18,470 --> 00:19:19,560
That's not fair to you.

308
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:35,190
You don't need me anymore?

309
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:37,560
I will always need you.

310
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:40,000
But Uncle,

311
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,710
to me,

312
00:19:43,430 --> 00:19:45,160
you're more than a guardian angel.

313
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:48,070
You're also the most important family member

314
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,000
I've left in the world.

315
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:51,680
I hope you can find something

316
00:19:51,710 --> 00:19:52,880
you want to do.

317
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:56,950
Do you understand what I'm talking about?

318
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:03,710
Not really.

319
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:07,310
Uncle.

320
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,560
I'm leaving for the capital city tomorrow.

321
00:20:12,470 --> 00:20:14,230
I will find those who want to kill me,

322
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:16,280
and I will explore my mom's stories.

323
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:18,880
I will live my life

324
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:19,880
better than anyone else in the world,

325
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,830
because that's what I want all along.

326
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:24,800
That's terrific.

327
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,760
I hope you can find something

328
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:29,070
you want to do.

329
00:20:30,350 --> 00:20:31,400
Live for yourself.

330
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:05,350
Find something I want to do.

