333
00:21:16,560 --> 00:21:18,040
Live for myself.

334
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:30,950
Uncle Wuzhu,

335
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:31,520
can you show up

336
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:32,560
normally?

337
00:21:33,040 --> 00:21:33,920
I remember.

338
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:38,350
Remember what?

339
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:40,040
Miss once said the same words

340
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:41,680
as you did this afternoon.

341
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,000
She wanted me

342
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,110
to find something I like.

343
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:45,070
Then have you found it?

344
00:21:47,280 --> 00:21:48,160
I want to open it.

345
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:04,310
It was left by miss back then.

346
00:22:04,950 --> 00:22:05,760
It's from my mother?

347
00:22:07,110 --> 00:22:08,000
What's in it?

348
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:08,950
I don't know.

349
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:10,830
You never opened it?

350
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:12,760
She never told me to open it.

351
00:22:13,110 --> 00:22:13,800
What now?

352
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:14,830
I've thought for a long time.

353
00:22:16,230 --> 00:22:17,000
In this world,

354
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,520
what I want to do most

355
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:19,950
is to open this box.

356
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:21,590
I want to see

357
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:22,680
what on earth did Miss leave.

358
00:22:23,710 --> 00:22:26,160
You must have been through a lot.

359
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:28,830
I've forgotten.

360
00:22:30,710 --> 00:22:32,830
Come on! Let's open it.

361
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:34,070
I don't have the key.

362
00:22:36,070 --> 00:22:36,830
Wait a minute.

363
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:47,280
Wait a minute. I'll go fetch another knife.

364
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:04,000
It's way too tough.

365
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:07,070
What's it made of?

366
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:08,280
I don't know.

367
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,350
How come it's so tough?

368
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:13,310
Where did my mom get it?

369
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:15,040
I've forgotten.

370
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:16,710
Where is the key?

371
00:23:17,560 --> 00:23:18,280
In the capital city.

372
00:23:19,230 --> 00:23:20,560
So, I will also go to the capital city.

373
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,800
Let's leave together tomorrow.

374
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:26,880
I'll leave first. Let's meet in the capital city.

375
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:29,040
What about this box?

376
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,160
You keep it.

377
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:35,160
What's it really made of?

378
