Girl.

379
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:00,920
Madam!

380
00:24:01,190 --> 00:24:03,880
Is Young Master gone by now?

381
00:24:03,950 --> 00:24:05,400
Let's go and have a look.

382
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:06,800
No need.

383
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:08,590
Yes.

384
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:23,400
He knows what he wants.

385
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:27,110
He'll leave eventually.

386
00:24:30,760 --> 00:24:31,520
Young Master!

387
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:53,040
I've told you I won't see you off.

388
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:55,560
You...

389
00:24:56,110 --> 00:24:58,070
It's not proper!

390
00:24:58,070 --> 00:24:58,830
Take care.

391
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:00,430
When I figure everything out,

392
00:25:00,430 --> 00:25:01,350
I will come back to pick you up.

393
00:26:10,950 --> 00:26:11,590
Young Master.

394
00:26:11,590 --> 00:26:13,470
The water is being heated.
It's gonna take a while before eating.

395
00:26:13,560 --> 00:26:14,640
That's fine. Go ahead and do your business.

396
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:15,880
I'm just walking around for a stretch.

397
00:26:16,190 --> 00:26:16,830
Yes!

398
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:19,350
Young Master!

399
00:26:22,470 --> 00:26:23,230
Young Master!

400
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,310
Young Master!

401
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,310
Teng...

402
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:42,470
Young Master, what's wrong?

403
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,310
Nothing.

404
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:49,430
Well,

405
00:26:50,590 --> 00:26:51,800
why are you here?

406
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:54,350
I also need to return to the capital city.

407
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:55,800
Didn't you ask me to spread the word that

408
00:26:55,800 --> 00:26:56,880
you're dead?

409
00:26:57,830 --> 00:26:58,470
Right.

410
00:26:59,190 --> 00:27:01,000
Officially, I was killed by you.

411
00:27:01,280 --> 00:27:02,280
I can't show my face in public.

412
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:03,470
So I follow you cavalry

413
00:27:04,470 --> 00:27:06,800
to avoid examination.

414
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:09,590
My guards know you?

415
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:10,560
No, they don't.

416
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:12,110
But they know what silver is.

417
00:27:12,590 --> 00:27:13,520
Why do you go to the capital city?

418
00:27:14,190 --> 00:27:15,000
It's none of your business.

419
00:27:16,070 --> 00:27:16,950
Fine with me.

420
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:19,950
I go to the capital city this time

421
00:27:20,190 --> 00:27:22,110
to find out who really wants to kill me.

422
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,830
It's Liu Ruyu, isn't it?

423
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:24,760
The second wife of your father?

424
00:27:25,110 --> 00:27:26,590
I want to know how she

425
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,710
misled the Investigator's Office.

426
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:28,590
I don't know that.

427
00:27:30,430 --> 00:27:31,430
You can help me find out.

428
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,640
When arriving in the capital city,
we can cooperate with each other.

429
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:35,760
Your death is the best cover.

430
00:27:36,430 --> 00:27:37,640
Why should I help you?

431
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,710
Don't you want to know who tricked you?

432
00:27:41,520 --> 00:27:42,560
No, I don't.

433
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,640
Now, you're asking me for a favor.

434
00:27:45,950 --> 00:27:46,640
Well then,

435
00:27:47,310 --> 00:27:48,520
I'll consider it when I reach the capital city.

436
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,560
Come back!

437
00:27:50,350 --> 00:27:51,560
Do you think

438
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:52,640
you are serious enough?

439
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,800
You have to prepare for your marriage
when you arrive in the capital city.

440
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:56,230
You won't have time for the investigation.

441
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:57,430
What marriage?

442
00:27:58,350 --> 00:28:00,160
Aren't you going to the capital city for getting married?

443
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,040
No one told you that?

444
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,110
No one did.

445
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:06,680
How did you know?

446
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:09,560
After receiving the secret order of killing you,

447
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:10,760
I have to know your information.

448
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:11,470
Just a quick glance.

449
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:12,760
Then whom am I going to marry?

450
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:13,640
I don't know.

451
00:28:13,830 --> 00:28:15,070
I was ordered to kill you,

452
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:16,000
not your whole family.

453
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,040
Why should I learn so much about you?

454
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:23,560
This

455
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:26,040
is my gift for your marriage.

456
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:28,230
Wish you a long and harmonious union,
and may you have a baby soon.

457
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:29,920
I'm going to make a fire.

458
00:28:51,470 --> 00:28:52,160
What are you doing?

459
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,800
The trade caravan coming toward us
belongs to the Investigator's Office.

460
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:13,020
=Fei Jie, director of the Third Division
of the Investigator's Office=

461
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:20,230
Luckily, I have sharp eyes.

462
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:21,920
Most men in that trade caravan

463
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:22,920
are from the Fourth Division.

464
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:25,230
Moreover,

465
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:26,950
powerful as your teacher,

466
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:28,110
he actually travels along to keep up the formation.

467
00:29:28,830 --> 00:29:29,760
I'm afraid something serious is happening.

468
00:29:31,830 --> 00:29:32,640
Stop!

469
00:29:33,800 --> 00:29:34,520
What are you doing?

470
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:42,590
Master Fei, we've checked.

471
00:29:42,590 --> 00:29:43,520
The inn is safe.

472
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:45,190
Good. Then we'll rest here.

473
00:29:45,190 --> 00:29:45,830
Yes.

474
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:52,520
I will walk around

475
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,400
to see if there's anything strange.

476
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:54,710
OK.

477
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,470
I know you'll follow me.

478
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:10,640
Where did you get this?

479
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,680
I took it from a fruit ranch nearby.

480
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,950
Where are you going?

481
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:18,830
Beiqi.

482
00:30:19,040 --> 00:30:19,760
Beiqi?

483
00:30:20,280 --> 00:30:22,190
Don't they always want to go to war with us?

484
00:30:22,190 --> 00:30:23,190
The war is coming.

485
00:30:24,190 --> 00:30:25,400
The Investigator's Office established
an intelligence network

486
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,800
in Beiqi years ago.

487
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:28,710
The performance was bad. They need a head.

488
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:29,710
So they send you there?

489
00:30:30,310 --> 00:30:32,520
Me? I'm only good at poisoning others.

490
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,640
I'm seeing someone off.

491
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,590
The one sitting in the carriage?

492
00:30:37,710 --> 00:30:38,400
Yes.

493
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:40,280
It's Yan Ruohai's son,

494
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:40,950
Yan Bingyun.

495
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:42,760
Really a promising young man.

496
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:45,400
How can you send such an excellent
young man to an enemy country?

497
00:30:46,710 --> 00:30:48,000
It's all because of you.

498
00:30:48,070 --> 00:30:48,880
Because of me?

499
00:30:49,950 --> 00:30:52,310
That Teng Zijing you killed is a scout of the Fourth Division.

500
00:30:53,470 --> 00:30:56,560
A member of the Fourth Division
actually tried to kill his superior.

501
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:59,470
Yan Ruohai must take the responsibility.

502
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,400
Teng Zijing

503
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:03,430
is under the command of his son Yan Bingyun.

504
00:31:03,430 --> 00:31:05,920
The Head was so angry that
he dismissed him from his post,

505
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,830
asking him to disguise with his men as trade caravan

506
00:31:09,830 --> 00:31:12,070
to take over the intelligence network in Beiqi.

507
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,400
It's pretty serious.

508
00:31:14,070 --> 00:31:16,400
I'm kind of seeing him off,
and kind of keeping up the formation.

509
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:20,280
I killed a member of our division. Am I in trouble?

510
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:23,110
Teng Zijing is not a regular member of the Investigator's Office.

511
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,640
He is relatively new to our office.

512
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,590
So it's no big deal.

513
00:31:26,040 --> 00:31:27,950
But you were lucky this time.

514
00:31:28,710 --> 00:31:29,430
What do you mean?

515
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:32,280
The Fourth Division is in charge of detection and patrol.

516
00:31:33,070 --> 00:31:34,470
The Sixth Division is the division responsible for assassination.

517
00:31:34,950 --> 00:31:37,160
Whoever wants to kill you didn't try hard enough.

518
00:31:37,280 --> 00:31:39,000
The fake order wasn't given to the Sixth Division,

519
00:31:39,310 --> 00:31:41,230
so the scout of the Fourth Division took action.

520
00:31:41,230 --> 00:31:42,560
If someone from the Sixth Division took the order,

521
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,430
then you were in real trouble.

522
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,430
I didn't know there are so many stories behind.

523
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:51,880
Well, you should go back.

524
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:53,350
And listen,

525
00:31:54,110 --> 00:31:56,800
no matter what happens, just wait till I'm back.

526
00:31:57,520 --> 00:31:58,000
Also,

527
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:00,000
next time you take pears,

528
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:02,950
do pick those big, fatty ones.

529
00:32:03,310 --> 00:32:05,190
Those are much sweeter.

530
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,110
Fan Xian.

531
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:29,680
Yan Bingyun.

532
00:32:36,230 --> 00:32:37,470
Do you stop me

533
00:32:37,470 --> 00:32:39,160
to avenge Teng Zijing's death?

534
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,400
Teng Zijing didn't deserve to die.

535
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,310
I already killed him. What do you want?

536
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,710
Give me the token for Director-General.

537
00:32:50,590 --> 00:32:52,040
So you want to take it by force?

538
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:56,640
Give it to me!

539
00:33:00,040 --> 00:33:00,800
Come on!

540
00:33:00,950 --> 00:33:01,920
Yan Bingyun.

541
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:05,710
You should remember the order you've taken.

542
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,400
You can't get off the carriage

543
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:10,310
before arriving in Beiqi.

544
00:33:10,950 --> 00:33:13,560
Fan Xian is cruel and mischievous.

545
00:33:14,110 --> 00:33:15,800
If he keeps the token,

546
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:18,520
the Investigator's Office
as well as Nanqing will be in danger.

547
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,710
If you get off this carriage,

548
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:25,040
our undercover operation in Beiqi will be ruined.

549
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:27,230
By then,

550
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,590
you will be the one

551
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,950
who puts Nanqing in danger.

552
00:33:32,230 --> 00:33:33,110
I won't get off the carriage.

553
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:35,160
You guys! Take his token for me.

554
00:33:35,800 --> 00:33:39,040
Whoever moves will be killed immediately.

555
00:33:46,310 --> 00:33:47,160
Let's go back.

556
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:53,830
That's right.

557
00:33:54,520 --> 00:33:55,950
Go back and rest.

558
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:57,400
We still have a long way to go tomorrow.

559
00:33:57,430 --> 00:34:00,560
Fan Xian, we'll meet again.

560
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:03,400
He won't be back for a minute.

561
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,120
Wait a moment!

562
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:40,040
Mr. Fan!

563
00:34:40,910 --> 00:34:41,100
It's a long way from Danzhou to the capital city.

564
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:43,000
=Wang Qinian, clerk of the Investigator's Office of Nanqing=
